{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_011mCkBWojKjC1Ww27GbNzQ6","type":"tool_result","content":"1\t# src/lib/agents — Agent Driver Abstraction\n2\t\n3\tPluggable agent driver system for wrapping external coding agents (Claude Code, Codex, OpenCode) behind a uniform `AgentDriver` interface. Each driver handles spawning, output parsing, health checks, and capability reporting.\n4\t\n5\t## Files\n6\t\n7\t| File | Purpose | Key Exports |\n8\t|------|---------|-------------|\n9\t| types.ts | AgentDriver interface and related types — DriverHealth, DriverCapabilities, DispatchOpts, OutputContract, plus deprecated SpawnOpts/AgentProcess/AgentEvent | `AgentDriver`, `DriverHealth`, `DriverCapabilities`, `DispatchOpts`, `OutputContract`, `TestResults`, `ACStatus` |\n10\t| stream-parser.ts | Stateless NDJSON stream parser — converts Claude API streaming events into typed `StreamEvent` objects | `parseStreamLine`, `StreamEvent`, `ToolStartEvent`, `ToolInputEvent`, `ToolCompleteEvent`, `TextEvent`, `RetryEvent`, `ResultEvent` |\n11\t| model-resolver.ts | Model resolution with 3-level cascade: task → agent → driver default | `resolveModel` |\n12\t| index.ts | Barrel re-exports for agents subsystem — types, stream parser, driver factory, model resolver | all public API |\n13\t\n14\t## Subdirectories — drivers/\n15\t\n16\t| File | Purpose | Key Exports |\n17\t|------|---------|-------------|\n18\t| drivers/factory.ts | Driver factory and module-singleton registry — register, retrieve, list, and reset drivers | `getDriver`, `registerDriver`, `listDrivers`, `resetDrivers` |\n19\t| drivers/claude-code.ts | Claude Code driver — in-process driver using the Agent SDK (no CLI spawning) | `ClaudeCodeDriver` |\n20\t| drivers/codex.ts | Codex driver — CLI-wrapped driver for OpenAI Codex, spawns `codex` binary and parses NDJSON stdout | `CodexDriver` |\n21\t| drivers/opencode.ts | OpenCode driver — CLI-wrapped driver for OpenCode, spawns `opencode` binary and parses NDJSON stdout | `OpenCodeDriver` |\n22\t| drivers/index.ts | Barrel re-exports — factory functions and all driver classes | all public API |\n23\t\n24\t## Tests\n25\t\n26\t| File | Purpose |\n27\t|------|---------|\n28\t| __tests__/types.test.ts | Type contract tests for AgentDriver interface |\n29\t| __tests__/stream-parser.test.ts | Stream parser tests — NDJSON event parsing for all StreamEvent types |\n30\t| __tests__/model-resolver.test.ts | Model resolver cascade tests |\n31\t| __tests__/index.test.ts | Barrel export verification tests |\n32\t| __tests__/claude-code-driver.test.ts | Claude Code driver tests |\n33\t| __tests__/codex-driver.test.ts | Codex driver tests |\n34\t| __tests__/opencode-driver.test.ts | OpenCode driver tests |\n35\t| __tests__/factory.test.ts | Driver factory/registry tests |\n36\t"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_01LUW5YMoYDRnUc9qHcGgcHp","session_id":"be33ba5d-0e81-49c4-ae53-e69ac56cd1fb","uuid":"e246e1cc-d8a8-4ebc-bd59-89137db2b693","timestamp":"2026-04-03T10:18:04.196Z"}
