{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01EBRrLxu4sVB9NC9jdb1wgb","type":"tool_result","content":"0\t# Session Retrospective — 2026-04-03\n1\t\n2\t**Session window:** ~2026-04-03T00:25 to ~2026-04-03T02:00 (approx. 95 minutes)\n3\t**Sprint progress:** 14/28 stories done (50%), Epics 1-4 complete\n4\t\n5\t---\n6\t\n7\t## 1. Session Summary\n8\t\n9\t| Story | Phases Run | Outcome | Notes |\n10\t|-------|-----------|---------|-------|\n11\t| 4-3-trace-id-generation-injection | verify (tail end) | **Done** | Was already at verify from prior session. 9/9 ACs passed. |\n12\t| 4-4-source-isolation-enforcement | create-story, dev, code-review, verify | **Done** | Full lifecycle in one session. 9/9 ACs, 100% coverage on module. |\n13\t| Epic 4 milestone | — | **Done** | All 4 stories shipped. Commit `4a35568`. |\n14\t| 5-1-flow-execution-sequential-steps | create-story, dev | **Review** | Story created and implemented. 31 tests, 89.91% coverage. Ran out of time before code-review/verify. |\n15\t\n16\t**Net output:** 2 stories completed + verified, 1 story implemented but not reviewed, 1 epic closed.\n17\t\n18\t---\n19\t\n20\t## 2. Issues Analysis\n21\t\n22\t### Bugs Found by Code Review (fixed)\n23\t\n24\t| Severity | Story | Issue |\n25\t|----------|-------|-------|\n26\t| HIGH | 4-3 | `generateTraceId` accepted NaN/Infinity/negative/float iteration values |\n27\t| HIGH | 4-4 | Path traversal via unsanitized `runId` in file path |\n28\t| HIGH | 4-4 | Silent file overwrite on basename collision — data loss risk |\n29\t| MEDIUM | 4-3 | No segment length cap — unbounded trace IDs possible |\n30\t| MEDIUM | 4-3 | `formatTracePrompt('')` produced empty trace marker silently |\n31\t| MEDIUM | 4-3 | `workflow-state.ts` coverage at 79.06%, below 80% floor |\n32\t| MEDIUM | 4-4 | Stale workspace contamination from crashed runs |\n33\t| MEDIUM | 4-4 | Missing edge case tests for sanitization/dedup |\n34\t\n35\tAll HIGH and MEDIUM bugs were fixed in the same session. Code review is earning its keep — 3 HIGH security/correctness bugs caught before merge.\n36\t\n37\t### Known LOW Issues (deferred)\n38\t\n39\t- 4-3: Duplicate trace ID guard missing; empty runId+taskName produces ugly ID; sanitizeSegment strips non-ASCII\n40\t- 4-4: `deduplicateFilename` counter loop unbounded; hardcoded `/tmp/` base path\n41\t\n42\t### Infrastructure Issues\n43\t\n44\t- **`codeharness verify` precondition failure:** The verify command checks global harness state flags (`tests_passed`, `coverage_met`) which are not set by manual test runs. Workaround: verify manually. This is a harness tooling gap.\n45\t- **`AGENTS.md` stale:** Verify command flags missing entries for new modules (`agent-dispatch.ts`, `agent-resolver.ts`, `session-manager.ts`, `trace-id.ts`, `source-isolation.ts`). Documentation debt accumulating — 5 modules behind now.\n46\t- **Pre-existing TS errors:** `src/commands/__tests__/run.test.ts` has 2 pre-existing type errors unrelated to current work.\n47\t\n48\t---\n49\t"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_012ujm5wbMMjNiJVhymSV3Q8","session_id":"be33ba5d-0e81-49c4-ae53-e69ac56cd1fb","uuid":"0cd3dec0-d22b-475a-90ef-b596fa5c179c","timestamp":"2026-04-03T10:20:09.780Z"}
